{"tid":1090052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憶述曾當面稱習近平為「king」　特朗普：他很喜歡 (14:30)","createTime":"2019-04-03T07:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T10:26:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9f68e9a68e61372048b52fbffb8379d791f380aa","tid":1090052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190403/s00004/d1a20234f126bd2c4190963466d6dcf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190403%2Fs00004%2Fd1a20234f126bd2c4190963466d6dcf7.jpg&h=6a995747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周二（2日）出席共和黨全國國會委員會晚宴時，憶述自己一年多前到訪北京期間，曾當面稱呼中國國家主席習近平為「king」，又說習近平喜歡這個稱呼。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，「習近平是個強勢的人，我稱呼他『king』，他說『我不是king，我是（國家）主席』（He said, 'But I am not king, I am president.'）；我說『不，你終身出任國家主席，所以你是king』。他說『哈』。他很喜歡，我與他相處不錯（I said 'No, you're president for life, and therefore you're king.' He said, huh. He liked that. I get along with him great.」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普曾於2017年11月到訪北京，翌年3月11日中國十三屆全國人大會議通過憲法修正案，刪除了國家主席連任兩屆的任期限制。<br />\n<br />\n（美國有線新聞網絡）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190403/s00004/1554270978560/憶述曾當面稱習近平為「king」-特朗普-他很喜歡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190403%2Fs00004%2F1554270978560%2F%E6%86%B6%E8%BF%B0%E6%9B%BE%E7%95%B6%E9%9D%A2%E7%A8%B1%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8Cking%E3%80%8D-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%BB%96%E5%BE%88%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5AEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=7cfd0f98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190403%2Fs00004%2F1554270978560%2F%E6%86%B6%E8%BF%B0%E6%9B%BE%E7%95%B6%E9%9D%A2%E7%A8%B1%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%82%BA%E3%80%8Cking%E3%80%8D-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%BB%96%E5%BE%88%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1&h=3bf87499\" target=\"_blank\">http